trashpanda (first_widemouth): “Aaaaah the fresh smell of the forest! Thank god I escaped the hustle and bustle of the suburbs for the quiet solitude of life in nature. I even found my very own tree hole to call home!
trashpanda (base): Just a few more trips back dumpster diving to find what I need to furnish it and I can kiss trash cans goodbye! Though I suppose while I’m back in the ‘burbs for a bit one more stroll into the city couldn't hurt.
trashpanda (shine): Maybe I’ll even find something fancy for my mantle…”